etheria.methods.getOwner(15,9).call(function(error, result) { console.log(result) });
```
result when working against infura (which is the correct response)
```
> etheria.methods.getOwner(15,9).call(function(error, result) { console.log(result) });
Promise { <pending> }
> 0xcf684DFB8304729355B58315E8019B1aa2AD1Bac
```
