```
I have verified that the firewall of the geth instance is off (ufw disabled) and that installing something like httpd or sshd on that computer shows ports 80 and 22 open on the host computer from the client computer. nmap never shows any other ports listening for connections.

Any thoughts here? It's highly likely I'm just doing something dumb. (I've been out of the game for a long time.)
